<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Welcome to Grecycle</title>
    <style>
        html,
        body {
            margin: 0 auto !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            height: 100% !important;
            width: 100% !important;
            background: #f1f1f1;
        }

        .hero {
            display: inline-block;
            align: center;
            width: 50%;
            background-color: lightgray;
        }

        .hero-content {
            padding: 20px 50px 20px 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="hero">
    <img src="cid:main" alt="" class="">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-title">Hi <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold"><%= username %></span>,</p>
        <p class=""> As of 2018, <span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">approximately 380 million tons of plastic is produced worldwide each year.</span> Our planet
            can't cope with this amount of plastic polluting the environment, and calls to reduce plastic pollution and
            consumption have increased in urgency in recent years!</p>
        <p class="">
            We are the problem and we are the solution.
        </p>
        <p class=""><span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold">Welcome to Grecycle</span> and donate your used resources like shampoo bottles, old newspapers or old
            batteries easily for the betterment of our planet Earth. Thank you for being part of our community and let's
            start recycling!</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>